author: wtopstaff
title: Presidents Cup Pairings
text:
By The Associated Press October 8, 2015 5:18 am Thursday At Jack Nicklaus Golf Club Korea Incheon, South Korea Yardage: 7,380; Par: 72 Fourballs 
8:35 p.m. — Dustin Johnson and Jordan Spieth, United States, vs. Louis Oosthuizen and Branden Grace, International. 
8:50 p.m. — Rickie Fowler and Jimmy Walker, United States, vs. Danny Lee and Sang-moon Bae, International. 
9:05 p.m. — Zach Johnson and Phil Mickelson, United States, vs. Adam Scott and Jason Day, International. 
9:20 p.m. — J.B. Holmes and Bubba Watson, United States, vs. Marc Leishman and Steven Bowditch, International. 
9:35 p.m. — Bill Haas and Chris Kirk, United States, vs. Thongchai Jaidee and Charl Schwartzel, International. Topics:
